Packages that use com.laoluade.ingestor.ao3.repositories
Package
Description
com.laoluade.ingestor.ao3.core
This package holds the core AO3 ingestion logic for the application.
com.laoluade.ingestor.ao3.repositories
This package defines the entities (table entry) and the repositories (databases) the Archive Server application uses to store persistent data.
com.laoluade.ingestor.ao3.services
This package contains the services that run the logic for the Archive Server application.
